snippet.title: Pick-ups: Sammy Atomiswave motherboard and Dolphin Blue
snippet.description: Finally got a Sammy Atomiswave motherboard, and I was actually able to track down an original Dolphin Blue cart, which I'm totally excited about being that this game is a bit hard to locate these days. I've the AW mobo running on my Pana Twin Long supergun and have the VGA output from the mobo hooked up to a Samsung SyncMaster 213T for the highest quality 640x480 picture that the motherboard is capable of displaying. Thanks so much for watching, hope you enjoy the video!
